abstract_ssm: The Fraternal organizations of Brooklyn collection includes material from chapters and lodges of ten fraternal organizations based in Brooklyn. Items in the collection include constitutions, bylaws, meeting proceedings, event programs, reports, newsletters, research journals, yearbooks, member lists, lodge rosters, and lodge directories.
